==English==
===Etymology===
{{blend|spoon|fork}}; originally a [[trademark]]

=== Pronunciation ===
*(''[[RP]]''): spôk, /spɔːk/, /spɔːk
*(''[[WEAE]]''): spôrk, /spork/, /spork/

=== Noun ===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# A eating [[utensil]] shaped like a spoon, the bowl of which is divided into [[prong]]s like those a fork, and so has the function of both [[implement]]s; some sporks have a [[serrated]] edge and so also function as a [[knife]].

